languages.text: "Приятно слышать, что, в отличие от несведущей черни, вы отдаете должное величию наших деяний, преподобный".
"It is a pleasure to hear that unlike the ignorant rabble, you give due acknowledgement to the greatness of our deeds, Confessor."
languages.original_text: "Приятно слышать, что, в отличие от несведущей черни, вы отдаете должное величию наших деяний, преподобный".

languages.text: « Contrairement aux masses ignorantes, vous reconnaissez le mérite de notre fonction comme il se doit. Vous m'en voyez ravie, confesseur. »
languages.original_text: "It is a pleasure to hear that unlike the ignorant rabble, you give due acknowledgement to the greatness of our deeds, Confessor."

traits.locale_text: « Contrairement aux masses ignorantes, vous reconnaissez le mérite de notre fonction comme il se doit. Vous m'en voyez ravie, révérend. »

languages.text: «Me complace oír que, a diferencia de la plebe ignorante, usted reconoce debidamente la grandeza de nuestro cometido, confesor».
languages.original_text: "It is a pleasure to hear that unlike the ignorant rabble, you give due acknowledgement to the greatness of our deeds, Confessor."

traits.locale_text: «Me complace oír que, a diferencia de la plebe ignorante, usted reconoce debidamente la grandeza de nuestro cometido, reverendo».

languages.text: “你与那些乌合之众截然不同，告解神父。你对我们的伟大使命给予了应有的认可，我很满意。”
languages.original_text: "It is a pleasure to hear that unlike the ignorant rabble, you give due acknowledgement to the greatness of our deeds, Confessor."

traits.locale_text: “你与那些乌合之众截然不同，牧师。你对我们的伟大使命给予了应有的认可，我很开心。”

languages.text: 「無知な有象無象と違って、私たちの行いの偉大さを認めてくださるとは、嬉しい限りです、聴罪師さん」
languages.original_text: "It is a pleasure to hear that unlike the ignorant rabble, you give due acknowledgement to the greatness of our deeds, Confessor."

traits.locale_text: 「無知な有象無象と違って、私たちの行いの偉大さを認めてくださるとは、嬉しい限りです、牧師様」

languages.text: "Es freut mich zu hören, dass Ihr im Gegensatz zum ignoranten Pöbel die Erhabenheit unserer Taten erkennt, Konfessor."
languages.original_text: "It is a pleasure to hear that unlike the ignorant rabble, you give due acknowledgement to the greatness of our deeds, Confessor."

traits.locale_text: "Es freut mich zu hören, dass Ihr im Gegensatz zum ignoranten Pöbel die Erhabenheit unserer Taten erkennt, Reverend."

languages.text: "Cahil ayaktakımının aksine, senin gayretlerimizin büyüklüğünü tanıdığını duymak büyük bir mutluluk Günah Çıkarıcı."
languages.original_text: "It is a pleasure to hear that unlike the ignorant rabble, you give due acknowledgement to the greatness of our deeds, Confessor."
